values:
still sick, still can't sleep. bleh it sucks, but what can ya do? i might drop out of summer school, you only get 3 credits for the summer, thats really pointless, i dunno i guess me & my mom should talk about it when she gets home. i wanna go for some chinese when she gets home, hopefully she'll want to do that. well just thought i'd rewrite this update, bc... i was sick of my bitchin in the other one.

♥ kitty

i really don't feel like making a new update. so i'm just rewriting what i had in here, my moms gone 3 more days. she'll be back monday after six. shes having fun i talked to her, shes happy. i just hope she comes back, i do miss her, but i'm living. i feel like i'm living on my own, & i have kids, since i've been babysitting. its really rough. lol but i'm handling it, i'm really depressed. i can feel it. but i'm trying so hard to fight it off trying to keep myself busy, & motivated, so it doesn't drown me in it. i'm trying to work through it, i really am. i just don't feel... happy, anymore.

♥ kitty
